&gt; Setup sw (once)
</p>

<p>
<code>git clone https://github.com/patrickbryant/ZZ4b.git</code>
</p>

<p>
&gt; Example job script  
cat /hildafs/home/alison/hh4b/main<sub>job.sh</sub>
</p>

<p>
Need to change seeds
</p>

<p>
 checks running jobs  
squeue
</p>

<p>
 Submit  
&gt; sbatch main<sub>job.sh</sub>
